- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the decidability of boundedness, which is a property related to the structure of the transition system. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the least likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the verification of properties of a system, which is a topic that can be related to machine learning.
